title: Amber Rose Flaunts Her Curves in Sexy Sheer Dress Following Split From Val Chmerkovskiy – See the Pics!
text: Amber Rose Flaunts Her Curves in Sexy Sheer Dress Following Split From Val Chmerkovskiy – See the Pics! by Desiree Murphy 11:48   INSTARimages Slay, Amber Rose! After calling it quits with Dancing With the Stars pro Val Chmerkovskiy earlier this month, the 33-year-old model is proving she's not letting a breakup get in the way of her fabulousness. The freshly single star sported a sheer black zip-up dress that highlighted her curvaceous figure for a night out at celebrity hotspot The Nice Guy in West Hollywood, California, on Tuesday. Photo: INSTARimages She paired the sexy frock with strappy stilettos, a black purse and gold statement earrings. Photo: AKM-GSI The outing comes less than a week after she debuted a new "Hollywood" arm tattoo via social media. "My new tattoo," she captioned a photo of her giant sleeve . "Great job @nikkohurtado." A post shared by Amber Rose (@amberrose) on Feb 15, 2017 at 5:36pm PST Meanwhile, ex Chmerkovskiy has been busy playing uncle to the newest member of his family, baby Shai. His brother, Maksim, welcomed the little bundle of joy last month with fiancée Peta Murgatroyd. Hear the 30-year-old dancer adorably gush over his "handsome" nephew in the video below!
